# Keep the Docker build context small and free of host artifacts/secrets.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.medusa
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
.turbo
**/.turbo

# Secrets — env is injected at runtime, never baked into the image
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Local-only data & transient exports
apps/backend/merge-backup-*.json
apps/backend/static
*-dump.sql
templates

# Docker / docs themselves don't belong in the context
Dockerfile
**/Dockerfile
docker-compose*.yml
DEPLOYMENT.md
**/.DS_Store
